Attrach

Hide files in the extended attributes of files on os x.

A single attribute is only allowed a small number of bytes,
but unlimited (?) attributes are allowed.
I'll add support for large files via multiple attributes, later.

----------

$ gpg -e file
$ rm file
$ ./attrach attach file.gpg pic.jpg
$ ls -l@ pic.jpg
  -rw-r--r--@ 1 james  staff  30 Nov 10 22:45 pic.jpg
          attrach  646
$ ./attrach get pic.jpg original.gpg

-james
